esidue behind.'<br>\n<small><b>Good Housekeeping<\/b><\/small>"}},"iconblocks_cLEaTx":{"type":"iconblocks","settings":{"icon_block_title":"The best smelling","icon_block_description":"'This is so brilliant - it's a delicious-smelling cleaner that you can use on everything'<br>\n<small><b>The Sunday Times<\/b><\/small>"}},"iconblocks_kkqVhL":{"type":"iconblocks","settings":{"icon_block_title":"The most enjoyable","icon_block_description":"'If you’re looking for luxurious cleaning vibes then Purdy & Figg take home the gold'<br>\n<small><b>The Daily Mail<\/b><\/small>"}}},"block_order":["iconblocks_C7PFq6","iconblocks_cLEaTx","iconblocks_kkqVhL"],"custom_css":[".green-btn {width: 343px; padding: 12px 16px; border-radius: 4px; margin-top: 40px; background-color: #604383 !important;}",".heading-2 {letter-spacing: 0px;}","@media (max-width: 768px) {.green-btn {margin-top: unset; width: 100% !important; max-width: 100% !important; } .pf-219-icon-block .icon-block-2 > div {display: block; } .icon-block-2 {padding-left: 0 !important; padding-right: 0 !important; }}"],"settings":{"class":"pf-219-icon-block","bg":"#ffffff","textcolor":"#212121","heading":"Hear what the press are saying about us...","show_hide_block":true,"showbtn":true,"btnbgcolor":"#11322c","btntxtcolor":"#ffffff","btntext":"GET OFFER","scrollto":"starterkit-product","top":"40","dataTrack":true,"targetUrl":"","index":7,"funnel_stage":"landing_page","dataModule":"membership_block","dataTitle":"get_my_free_scent","eventValue":"shop_anchor","itemId":"","optionIndex":"","ItemName":""}},"faq_section_reskin_FjUHQw":{"type":"faq-section-reskin","blocks":{"text_8dxAFi":{"type":"text","settings":{"open":true,"faq-question":"How do I use Counter Clean?","faq-ans":"<p>To use Counter Clean, simply pour the whole 20ml bottle of cleaning concentrate into your Bottle for Life and slowly fill to the top (just below the neck) with tap water. Give the bottle a gentle shake to mix, then enjoy your uplifting clean!<\/p>"}},"text_jjfD6j":{"type":"text","settings":{"open":false,"faq-question":"Which surfaces is Counter Clean suitable for?","faq-ans":"<p>We're pleased to say that Counter Clean is pH neutral, which means it’s safe to use on most surfaces. That includes softer materials like aluminium, wood, stone, quartz and other sealed surfaces. We do recommend patch testing first on any particularly sensitive or precious surfaces you’re concerned about. Just spray onto a cloth and wipe a small patch to see the results. <\/p>"}},"text_qdgxrE":{"type":"text","settings":{"open":false,"faq-question":"How do I manage my subscription?","faq-ans":"<p>We offer lots of subscription options, including switching your scent refill pack, changing the frequency of your deliveries or cancelling your membership altogether. Subscriptions are set to a 90-day frequency by default, but you can always move your next billing date if you need to in a few easy steps. We understand there might be times when you need to stop your deliveries, and we’ll always respect your decision to leave - even if we’ll miss you.<\/p><p>If you have any trouble managing your subscription, our Customer Experience Team is always on hand to respond to your questions and requests as soon as possible. They’re very friendly.<\/p>"}},"text_j6PQrb":{"type":"text","disabled":true,"settings":{"open":false,"faq-question":"What's the difference between Signature & Seasonal?","faq-ans":"<p>We offer two different scent collections with your Counter Clean subscription - Signature and Seasonal Scents. Our Signature Scent pack is available all year round, and contains our three best-selling scents - Uplifting Citrus, Balancing Floral, and Grounding Vetiver. Our Seasonal Scent pack contains three limited edition new scents blended for every season. <\/p>"}},"text_z6MmLP":{"type":"text","settings":{"open":false,"faq-question":"How many uses will I get out of a bottle?","faq-ans":"<p>A 300ml bottle of Counter Clean (including one 20ml concentrate) contains about 230 sprays. A typical household will get through one of our 300ml bottles in two to four weeks, unless you get a bit addicted to wiping down your surfaces like we have!<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["text_8dxAFi","text_jjfD6j","text_qdgxrE","text_j6PQrb","text_z6MmLP"],"custom_css":[".green-btn {margin-top: 80px !important; background-color: #604383 !important; font-size: 16px;}",".heading-2 {letter-spacing: 0px;}","@media (max-width: 768px) {.green-btn {margin-top: 32px !important; width: 100% !important; max-width: 100% !important; }}"],"settings":{"enable":true,"color_bg":"#fafafa","class":"","heading":"Frequently asked questions","addScrollBtn":true,"scrollBtnText":"GET OFFER","scrollto":"starterkit-product","top":"40","dataTrack":true,"targetUrl":"","index":8,"funnel_stage":"landing_page","dataModule":"faq","dataTitle":"get_my_free_scent","eventValue":"shop_anchor","itemId":"","optionIndex":"","ItemName":""}},"footer_2_gaj6Fd":{"type":"footer-2","custom_css":["@media (max-width: 768px) {.footer-2 .d-flex > div {text-align: left; }}"],"settings":{}}},"order":["announcement_bar_reskin_rmNQpU","banner_290_RyF93t","review_blocks_343_dJTAAN","icon_blocks_reskin_3WFfKz","image_with_listing_8niYrP","media_with_text_6Mbyc9","buy_box_v3_ULhXmA","scent_tabs_383_eiibB4","full_width_image_text_KAAiQY","icon_blocks_reskin_290_4PTC7H","faq_section_reskin_FjUHQw","footer_2_gaj6Fd"]}